import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import { BorderedRadio, Radio, RadioGroup, Sans } from '../src'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"radiogroup"}}>{`RadioGroup`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"default"}}>{`Default`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<RadioGroup>
  <Radio value="SHIP">Provide shipping address</Radio>
  <Radio value="PICKUP">Arrange for pickup</Radio>
</RadioGroup>`} __scope={{props,BorderedRadio,Radio,RadioGroup,Sans}}>
  <RadioGroup>
    <Radio value="SHIP">Provide shipping address</Radio>
    <Radio value="PICKUP">Arrange for pickup</Radio>
  </RadioGroup>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"with-default-value"}}>{`With default value`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<RadioGroup defaultValue="SHIP">
  <Radio value="SHIP">Provide shipping address</Radio>
  <Radio value="PICKUP">Arrange for pickup</Radio>
</RadioGroup>`} __scope={{props,BorderedRadio,Radio,RadioGroup,Sans}}>
  <RadioGroup defaultValue="SHIP">
    <Radio value="SHIP">Provide shipping address</Radio>
    <Radio value="PICKUP">Arrange for pickup</Radio>
  </RadioGroup>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"disabled-with-default-value"}}>{`Disabled with default value`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={2} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<RadioGroup defaultValue="SHIP" disabled>
  <Radio value="SHIP">Provide shipping address</Radio>
  <Radio value="PICKUP">Arrange for pickup</Radio>
</RadioGroup>`} __scope={{props,BorderedRadio,Radio,RadioGroup,Sans}}>
  <RadioGroup defaultValue="SHIP" disabled>
    <Radio value="SHIP">Provide shipping address</Radio>
    <Radio value="PICKUP">Arrange for pickup</Radio>
  </RadioGroup>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"bordered-radiogroup"}}>{`Bordered RadioGroup`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={3} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<RadioGroup defaultValue="SHIP">
  <BorderedRadio value="SHIP">Provide shipping address</BorderedRadio>
  <BorderedRadio value="PICKUP">
    Arrange for pickup
    <Sans size="2" color="black60">
      After you place your order, you’ll be appointed an Artsy Specialist
      within 2 business days to handle pickup logistics.
    </Sans>
  </BorderedRadio>
</RadioGroup>`} __scope={{props,BorderedRadio,Radio,RadioGroup,Sans}}>
  <RadioGroup defaultValue="SHIP">
    <BorderedRadio value="SHIP">Provide shipping address</BorderedRadio>
    <BorderedRadio value="PICKUP">
      Arrange for pickup
      <Sans size="2" color="black60">
        After you place your order, you’ll be appointed an Artsy
        Specialist within 2 business days to handle pickup logistics.
      </Sans>
    </BorderedRadio>
  </RadioGroup>
</Playground></MDXTag>
